import React from 'react';
import { Row, Col, Card, Button } from 'react-bootstrap';
import MainScreen from '../../components/MainScreen/MainScreen';

const Tareas = () => {
    return (
        <MainScreen title="Tareas de Administrador">
            <Row>
                <Col>
                    <Card style={{ height: '30%' }}>
                        <Card.Header as="h3">Restaurantes</Card.Header>
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Agregar y Editar Restaurantes</Card.Title>
                            <Card.Text>
                                With supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.
                            </Card.Text>
                            <Button variant="primary" className='text-warning'>Go somewhere</Button>
                        </Card.Body>
                    </Card>

                    <Card>
                        <Card.Header as="h3">Usuarios</Card.Header>
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Agregar y Editar Usuarios</Card.Title>
                            <Card.Text>
                                With supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.
                            </Card.Text>
                            <Button variant="primary" className='text-warning'>Go somewhere</Button>
                        </Card.Body>
                    </Card>

                    <Card>
                        <Card.Header as="h3">Reportes</Card.Header>
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Reportes de todos los restaurantes</Card.Title>
                            <Card.Text>
                                With supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.
                            </Card.Text>
                            <Button variant="primary" className='text-warning'>Go somewhere</Button>
                        </Card.Body>
                    </Card>
                </Col>

                <Col>
                    foto
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </MainScreen>
    )
}

export default Tareas
